headline: Ask HN: Strange Errors on Apple ID
description:
Getting some weird errors on https://appleid.apple.com/ thoughts?

Cookie “myacinfo” has been rejected because it is already expired. appleid.apple.com Cookie “awat” has been rejected because it is already expired. appleid.apple.com Cookie “caw” has been rejected because it is already expired. appleid.apple.com Cookie “caw-at” has been rejected because it is already expired. appleid.apple.com Layout was forced before the page was fully loaded. If stylesheets are not yet loaded this may cause a flash of unstyled content. common-header.js:1:8187 XML Parsing Error: no root element found Location: https://appleid.apple.com/account/manage/gs/ws/token Line Number 1, Column 1: token:1:1 Content Security Policy: Ignoring ‘x-frame-options’ because of ‘frame-ancestors’ directive. Relative positioning of table rows and row groups is now supported. This site may need to be updated because it may depend on this feature having no effect. signin
headline_zh-Hans: Ask HN: 苹果ID出现奇怪的错误
headline_zh-Hant: Ask HN: 蘋果ID出現奇怪的錯誤
description_zh-Hans:
在 https://appleid.apple.com/ 上遇到一些奇怪的错误？

Cookie "myacinfo "已被拒绝，因为它已经过期。appleid.apple.com Cookie "awat "已被拒绝，因为它已经过期。appleid.apple.com Cookie "caw "已被拒绝，因为它已经过期。appleid.apple.com Cookie "caw-at "已被拒绝，因为它已经过期。appleid.apple.com 在页面完全加载之前，布局被强制。如果样式表尚未加载，这可能会导致无样式的内容闪现。 common-header.js:1:8187 XML解析错误：没有找到根元素 位置：https://appleid.apple.com/account/manage/gs/ws/token 第1行，第1列：token:1:1 内容安全政策。忽略'x-frame-options'，因为有'frame-ancestors'指令。 现在支持表的行和行组的相对定位。这个网站可能需要更新，因为它可能依赖于这个功能没有效果。 登录
description_zh-Hant:
